  <chunk id="524020333ab93c945ffd02838cb08672703724c1.c3" text="Conclusions/Significance: This antibody display platform will complement existing technologies by virtue of providing properties unique to lentiviruses and antibody expression in human cells, which, in turn, may aid the discovery of novel therapeutic human mAbs.">
